---
title: Creamy Mustard, Bacon & Courgette Spaghetti with Parmesan & Apple Salad
description: Golden ropes of spaghetti have been coated in a rich, creamy mustard sauce with tender courgette soaking up all the flavours. Nuggets of bacon add the perfect savoury note, and with a scattering of sharp Parmesan cheese and a fresh salad, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.
